divs: Sighting DetailsStanding on my back pourch i alway look up at the sky and watch the stars. Thats when i noticed a bright star like object moving very slow. i watched it for about 3 minutes. I thought it was a plain but it had no other light or any blinking. it didnt make any noise. The object then started to speed up like a shooting star and was moving very fast i watched it for about a min. mabe less until it was gone.
